name: r-longitudinaldata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '2.4.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-longitudinaldata
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/longitudinalData_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/longitudinalData/longitudinalData_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6d8b155726b5e1913711c84af3e0fc56bb3a1097e0471628572b88239f63db52

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 3
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - {{ cdt('mesa-libgl-devel') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('mesa-dri-drivers') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libselinux') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxdamage') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxxf86vm') }}  # [linux]
    - xorg-libxfixes           # [linux]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-class
    - r-clv
    - r-misc3d
    - r-rgl
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-class
    - r-clv
    - r-misc3d
    - r-rgl

test:
  requires:
    - xorg-libxfixes  # [linux]
  commands:
    - LD_LIBRARY_PATH=${BUILD_PREFIX}/x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/usr/lib64:${BUILD_PREFIX}/lib $R -e "library('longitudinalData')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('longitudinalData')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http:www.r-project.org
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Tools for longitudinal data and joint longitudinal data (used by packages kml and
    kml3d).
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
